com.sun.tools.visualvm.core.snapshot

Class SnapshotCategory<X extends Snapshot>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.tools.visualvm.core.snapshot.SnapshotCategory<X>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Positionable

    public abstract class SnapshotCategory<X extends Snapshot>
extends Object
implements Positionable
    Category describing a snapshot type. Category should return POSITION_NONE for getPreferredPosition() if it's not to be shown in UI.
    Author:
    Jiri Sedlacek, Tomas Hurka
